{"tid":378273,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[GOT][睇哂先好入]屌你老母咩就咁樣整死","createTime":"2017-08-28T11:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T12:57:20.000Z","uid":82889,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"767357afdbded9356745f1e70e8349ab107853e0","tid":378273,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咩就咁樣整死little finger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆你個街個劇情直接係前幾集做都得啦<br />\n都係格鳩硬砌撚死佢咋嘛,仲要野都唔比佢講多幾句就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本鳩生lf黎到呢季做d野已經好撚柒<br />\n個個一係打war一係打great war,係得lf仲玩緊前幾季d陰謀<br />\n好明顯個編劇都唔知點樣塞鳩佢落去主線到好,唯有將佢當支線搞店佢算<br />\n<br />\n但咁撚樣就砌鳩死佢會唔會過鳩份左d啊大佬<br />\n話哂上季定上兩季都拖馬黎幫jon拎番winterfell<br />\n原來而家一次過嗡哂佢之前d罪行同埋bran個痴線佬鳩嗡幾句佢就會冇撚哂勢力<br />\n屌咁你不如季頭就一刀插撚死佢啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09019416c25bb0c6acf3e392df1b506648442d34","tid":378273,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:11:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b042ab039b6ffce72212bf122a3c51cab85d5a40","tid":378273,"uid":16624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"只能話，一直冇好理由殺佢，sansa亦殺佢唔落手。<br />\n<br />\n而家佢挑撥兩姐妹罪證確鑿，咁就一舖清算。如果lf冇挑撥，sansa就唔殺佢。"},{"pid":"5523bb3299643d7b5ecb45dd4a150fa2000e8aa0","tid":378273,"uid":82889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只能話，一直冇好理由殺佢，sansa亦殺佢唔落手。<br />\n<br />\n而家佢挑撥兩姐妹罪證確鑿，咁就一舖清算。如果lf冇挑撥，sansa就唔殺佢。</blockquote><br />\nlf會係sansa面前講到咁撚出面已經係弱智化左佢"},{"pid":"3b8b760433148659da12f83cf1b1c0bf947dc05c","tid":378273,"uid":119223,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"雖知LF呢條仆街係罪有應得<br />\n但個審判過程真係好不公同兒戲<br />\n重可憐過當年imp，連比武審判既機會都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsansa : 呢度唔係法庭，唔需要證據<br />\n<br />\nbran : 我對眼就係證據 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b22832ccc14b526135752da0352f5d707198d5","tid":378273,"uid":16624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>只能話，一直冇好理由殺佢，sansa亦殺佢唔落手。<br />\n<br />\n而家佢挑撥兩姐妹罪證確鑿，咁就一舖清算。如果lf冇挑撥，sansa就唔殺佢。</blockquote><br />\nlf會係sansa面前講到咁撚出面已經係弱智化左佢</blockquote><br />\n冇小說backup，早就弱智晒變平民"},{"pid":"6b6ee6157ac5e19cd4e529027f99ba014ea9558a","tid":378273,"uid":82889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:21:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖知LF呢條仆街係罪有應得<br />\n但個審判過程真係好不公同兒戲<br />\n重可憐過當年imp，連比武審判既機會都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsansa : 呢度唔係法庭，唔需要證據<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">bran : 我對眼就係證據 </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一開始仲心諗bran坐係到想點撚樣"},{"pid":"8985efcc934c2cfa98f6702645ad6bb365bfa7c9","tid":378273,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4addf8241601ed9e5b055e1a2819b64fd98f988c","tid":378273,"uid":82889,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>只能話，一直冇好理由殺佢，sansa亦殺佢唔落手。<br />\n<br />\n而家佢挑撥兩姐妹罪證確鑿，咁就一舖清算。如果lf冇挑撥，sansa就唔殺佢。</blockquote><br />\nlf會係sansa面前講到咁撚出面已經係弱智化左佢</blockquote><br />\n冇小說backup，早就弱智晒變平民</blockquote><br />\n其實sansa殺arya對他有甚麼好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成個角色去到呢季已經冇哂動機可言<br />\n當初就算唔知佢動機,但睇佢d陰謀都好正<br />\n但而家講到去great war,係呢個大背景下佢仲玩呢d野已經好無聊<br />\nchaos is a ladder<br />\n但到底佢想爬去邊?完全冇交代就死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65d101cfcd8d4f8b2260f764611205561ceeddd","tid":378273,"uid":48130,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:37:08.000Z","msg":"佢由頭到尾都係想坐Iron throne 同娶Sansa做老婆, 佢咁多季都講左好多次呢樣野<br />\n<br />\nArya係其中一個障礙, 佢今季都已經想做低LF, LF要除去Arya好正常<br />\n<br />\n套劇係寫得差, 但係如果連咁簡單既野都睇唔明就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b72eb28676dfe5157c7588a564cf2129ebaccc7","tid":378273,"uid":48130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全認同....完全沒有證據就可以判死刑，連他的下屬也背叛他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYohn Royce不嬲都好憎LF, 不過齋睇電視唔會知呢樣野<br />\n<br />\nLF係個外人, 靠娶左Lysa先做到lord protector of the Vale<br />\n<br />\nYohn Royce呢個Vale既一個大領主點會鍾意比外人統治, 佢自己都想做個個位"},{"pid":"b78bb70cd8adf9b780c2912ce30cd91b5ddddebc","tid":378273,"uid":82889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢由頭到尾都係想坐Iron throne 同娶Sansa做老婆, 佢咁多季都講左好多次呢樣野<br />\n<br />\nArya係其中一個障礙, 佢今季都已經想做低LF, LF要除去Arya好正常<br />\n<br />\n套劇係寫得差, 但係如果連咁簡單既野都睇唔明就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢咁既勢力仲學人想坐Iron throne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a27e087df7788f773328459ab76da9ee3cc529","tid":378273,"uid":48130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢由頭到尾都係想坐Iron throne 同娶Sansa做老婆, 佢咁多季都講左好多次呢樣野<br />\n<br />\nArya係其中一個障礙, 佢今季都已經想做低LF, LF要除去Arya好正常<br />\n<br />\n套劇係寫得差, 但係如果連咁簡單既野都睇唔明就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢咁既勢力仲學人想坐Iron throne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢由一個咩都冇既人去到臨死前係lord of harrenhal, lord paramount of the trident同lord protector of the vale, 冇勢力?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98578218fee06c45b7af582997d564d6ef82829","tid":378273,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deb456b000479753c8c631ba2ed3fc4d7626c9bb","tid":378273,"uid":16624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢由頭到尾都係想坐Iron throne 同娶Sansa做老婆, 佢咁多季都講左好多次呢樣野<br />\n<br />\nArya係其中一個障礙, 佢今季都已經想做低LF, LF要除去Arya好正常<br />\n<br />\n套劇係寫得差, 但係如果連咁簡單既野都睇唔明就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢咁既勢力仲學人想坐Iron throne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢由一個咩都冇既人去到臨死前係lord of harrenhal, lord paramount of the trident同lord protector of the vale, 冇勢力?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLittle finger個名都係因為俾人串又細又廢，撈到上去全靠權謀，想做王有咩出奇"},{"pid":"3b5dcf6210c660a9c063df698d2305aa889ddd24","tid":378273,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abb421a1a08e344e89efaa694aa974c59016670a","tid":378273,"uid":48130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢由頭到尾都係想坐Iron throne 同娶Sansa做老婆, 佢咁多季都講左好多次呢樣野<br />\n<br />\nArya係其中一個障礙, 佢今季都已經想做低LF, LF要除去Arya好正常<br />\n<br />\n套劇係寫得差, 但係如果連咁簡單既野都睇唔明就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n他也說自己很喜歡cat stark呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你相信嗎？</blockquote><br />\n點會唔信, 佢為左Cat可以同Brandon Stark決鬥<br />\nLysa親佢重傷同佢做愛佢都以為係Cat比左隻豬佢<br />\n佢殺Lysa之前都係講佢只愛Cat<br />\n<br />\n點會唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80bf823296673e8c3aa615e651d1a85eaa03363","tid":378273,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢由頭到尾都係想坐Iron throne 同娶Sansa做老婆, 佢咁多季都講左好多次呢樣野<br />\n<br />\nArya係其中一個障礙, 佢今季都已經想做低LF, LF要除去Arya好正常<br />\n<br />\n套劇係寫得差, 但係如果連咁簡單既野都睇唔明就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢咁既勢力仲學人想坐Iron throne<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢由一個咩都冇既人去到臨死前係lord of harrenhal, lord paramount of the trident同lord protector of the vale, 冇勢力?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好意思我話佢既勢力係指佢實際既勢力<br />\n佢真係有咁多人企佢果邊今集就唔會咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最大最大問題係,我睇唔出佢既死係之後會有咩大影響<br />\n佢死左有冇人會黎報仇?下季仲會唔會有關佢事既劇情?我就咁睇就係冇啦<br />\n當然以凡人奮鬥黎講佢的確係靠所謂機靈黎拎到今時今日既地位<br />\n但佢最後得番黎既野原來係不堪一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e0545922cf6103fed4e8db98c5ff03eacc5fb1","tid":378273,"uid":48130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢由頭到尾都係想坐Iron throne 同娶Sansa做老婆, 佢咁多季都講左好多次呢樣野<br />\n<br />\nArya係其中一個障礙, 佢今季都已經想做低LF, LF要除去Arya好正常<br />\n<br />\n套劇係寫得差, 但係如果連咁簡單既野都睇唔明就真係<img src=\"/asset